e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"Why ISO 9001 Certification in UAE | ISO 9001 Certification In Dubai | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"No matter the size of the organization, ISO 9001 certification for Quality management system (QMS) offers umpteen benefits. Acquiring ISO certification can"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"Why every company must have ISO 9001 Certification?"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"Why ISO 9001 Certification in UAE | ISO 9001 Certification In Dubai | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"No matter the size of the organization, ISO 9001 certification for Quality management system (QMS) offers umpteen benefits. Acquiring ISO certification can"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/why-every-company-must-have-iso-9001-certification"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:40+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Why ISO 9001 Certification in UAE | ISO 9001 Certification In Dubai | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"No matter the size of the organization, ISO 9001 certification for Quality management system (QMS) offers umpteen benefits. Acquiring ISO certification can"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L21","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"2. Improve the consistency of your operation"}]
11:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Consistency is nothing but reducing the unwanted changes in your operations. Customer does not like inconsistency or variation in the product. Every customer likes the product supplied by the vendor to be same or consistent all the time. To maintain consistency there should be increased control over the product or processes."}]
12:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"3. To get more business"}]
13:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Once you get ISO 9001:2015 certified, you can showcase your certification to get business from new customers. With ISO 9001:2015 certification can open you with new opportunities which you were not able to get when you were not certified."}]
14:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"4. To get better product quality"}]
15:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Quality is nothing but the degree of excellence of something. Improvement in product quality is desired by all the customers. Thus the reason for adopting quality management system should be to improve the quality of the entire organization."}]
16:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"5. Increase customer satisfaction with your product"}]
17:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The customers are satisfied when their vendors supply their quality products. If your QMS is working correctly means there are fewer complaints regarding your products and you know exactly what your customer wants will lead to increased customer satisfaction. Increased customer satisfaction and efficient organizations will tend to increase the value of your shareholders"}]
18:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"6. Manage your company processes effectively"}]
19:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The quality management services connect the inter-related processes to form a whole united bundle to ensure that processes are not managed individually but rather collectively. It is important to describe and understand your company processes. ISO 9001:2015 provides you with guidelines to think systematically about your processes resulting in the more effective management of your company’s processes."}]
1a:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"7. To boost employee morale"}]
1b:["$","p","18",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 9001:2015 quality management systems can make employees more confident and give them the power to do something. Your QMS will provide the employees with quality objectives, properly documented instructions and quick feedback. This will improve the work culture of the organization."}]
1c:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"8. Reduce the costs of your organization"}]
1d:["$","p","20",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Your organization wastes a lot of money on repair, rework, rejected products, and many more things. With an ISO certification for your organization will see fewer problems with your organization's products and thus do rework will not be required resulting in saving more money."}]
1e:["$","p","21",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"How to get ISO 9001 Certification in Dubai"}]
1f:["$","p","22",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Choose the best ISO consultancy in Dubai to get ISO 9001 certification for your organization. With a team of industry experts, Wizms is undoubtedly one of the best ISO certification consultancies in UAE with an impeccable track record of helping companies to acquire the ISO 9001 certificate quickly and easily. We help you get through the hassle-free procedure that allows your firm to obtain ISO certification within very less time."}]
20:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"Why every company must have ISO 9001 Certification?"}]]}]}]
